desc: A safe spiritual space where healing can begin. Do Spirituality 'YOUR WAY'. Crystals, sage, incense, crystal jewelry, salt lamps, oils, and more! Reiki, Intuitive Healing, and Human Design practitioners available in person and online. Join the 11:11 Friendly movement! Co-create your own faith and belief system!!!

layout.text: A safe space where healing begins… Located in Ridgewood, NJ, our boutique and studio offer a safe space to explore spirituality. We offer an array of products and services to support healing and manifesting from within. 10 Miles outside of NYC, our location is accessible to NJ Transit (train & bus).
